<p>[2] Daniel Simon, ed. Dispatches from the Republic of Letters: 50 Years of the Neustadt International Prize for Literature, 1970–2020, Dallas, Texas: Phoneme Media / Deep Vellum, 2020.</p>
<p>[3] Dispatches from the Republic of Letters, p. 5. </p>
<p>[4] Dispatches from the Republic of Letters, p. 65. </p>
<p>[5] Dispatches from the Republic of Letters, p. 67.</p>
<p>[6] Dispatches from the Republic of Letters, p. 4. </p>
